00039 \section what What is SAGE III?
00040 
00041    Sage III is the 3rd iteration of an intermediate representation well suited to
00042    source-to-source level processing of high level languages (C++, in particular).
00043    Sage III is used within the ROSE project and had been developed as part of the 
00044    ROSE project using parts of the original Sage II source code.  Substantial work 
00045    has gone into SAGE III, beyond that done in Sage II.  We would like to thank
00046    the original Sage developers to there work.
00047 
00048  */
